library(fitibble)
minute_data <- read_rds("../../data/prep/minute_data__export_2.rds") %>% 
  fitibble()
n <- 10
id_ <- unique(minute_data$id)
index <- round(seq(0, length(id_), length.out = n))
p <- list()
for(i in 1:(n - 1)) {
  p[[i]] <- minute_data %>% 
    filter(id %in% id_[(index[i] + 1):index[i + 1]]) %>% 
    plot_missingness(calendar_time = F)
}
p
